    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing consistent with regular road use. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, though there is some light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in strong health with a consistent idle and smooth gear transitions. It has benefited from regular synthetic oil changes, and the cooling system was recently inspected and flushed. The tires are at roughly 70% tread life, and the brake pads have plenty of material remaining. This is a reliable, honest car that has been cared for and is ready for the road. I have the service records on hand and welcome any independent mechanical inspection.",
